item.title: Fucking alot of people cant connect
item.dc:creator: @marcbob marcbob
item.description:
@marcbob wrote:

You really should stop posting this but on topic-

The people you gave the client dl to probably dont have the one with your ip in it. Make sure you change the client to connect to your ip in gui and compile. Then you gotta compress your client into .rar and upload to a file sharing site like uppit or mediafire.

Otherwise if your sure its not the ip then it is either your portforwarding or firewall. Make sure your firewall is off which may sound risky because it is but I had to do it to host a server and if that still doesnt fix it then the problem is your portforwarding which is only allowing certain kinds of connections
